reviewText: When the disc was placed in my (new) Panasonic Blue-Ray disc player, it indicated "No PLAY", indicating a viewing restriction, even though player settings indicated no limitation on age of viewers or restrictions on content.  Furthermore, other discs equally uncensored played with no problems.  So -- I would welcome the opportunity to review this film, but as of now it is Uncut, Uncensored & Unplayable.
